name: Oversized Clothing Collection
description:
Patreon

Get early access to build and test build, be able to try all epochs and test them by yourself on Patreon or contact me for support on Discord

Recommended settings

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras (Recommended for best quality, you may try other samplers)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 10

  • LORA weight for txt2img: reccomended 0.2-0.5.

Insutrctions

My advice is to start with posted images prompt.

Also, for each model, look on version description and on keywords on the right panel.

Enjoy!

If you'd like to support my efforts and have access to early and bleeding edge builds, please think about joining my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/betterCuteAsians

modelVersions.name: Sweater/Hoodie
modelVersions.description:
This LoRA is very easy to use, usually works with any color, just repeat the keyword with the color, like "oversized_sweater, red oversized_sweater"

In my images i gave a weight of 1.3 to the keyword oversized_sweater or hoodie, and i placed the keyword at the beginning of the prompt.

Most of the images of the training are with hoddie/sweater with naked legs, but some of them have boots or stocking, so if you want them you might try to add it to your prompt.

Checkpoint used to generate the images: Chillout

modelVersions.name: T-Shirt
modelVersions.description:
Somehow i couldn't manage to select the color of the shirt or to have sports or colorful shirts, most of the times it just generate a white empty shirt but there is not a single one empty white shirt in the training model so i really don't know. maybe it just need an higher weight. If you find a good prompt post it for the others please, thanks in advance.

In my images i gave a weight of 1.3 to the keyword oversized_shirt, and i placed the keyword at the beginning of the prompt.

There are a few images in the training with "back_view" keyword but it doesn't always work, you might try it and give an higher weight if necessary.

There are also many images with "colorful" keyword, you might try it with higher possible weight and hope for a lucky seed.

I posted epoch 10, maybe with other epochs all these problems disappear, if you want to try all epochs come in my patreon and get Edge Access.

Checkpoint used to generate the images: Chillout for realistic ones/Yesmix for anime ones

modelVersions.description:

Works great with 1shoulder dress to make a jumper 1 shoulder dress.

Works great with crop top model to have a crop top dress that is basically a cutted jumper dress.

Works great with colorful dress to have a jumper rainbow color dress.

Works also with anime.

modelVersions.name: Jacket
modelVersions.description:
Try to start your prompt with you girl model and then "(wearing oversized_jacket:1.3)" might work without any weight but in my experienced gives best result with 1.3 weight on the keyword and 0.5 weight on the model.
